// Page FirstVisit Text :
"P1231046489" "This is a copy of today's paper."
// Answer Text :
"P4060782435" "Leave"
// Page HelloPage Text :
"P3388392127" "You watch as a series of letters appears magically in front of you.  The letters spell out a rather personalized message .<br><br><scale 1.1><font face=computer><color BurlyWood>'{HeroName}, this is Doc Quantum contacting you.  I believe you may be aware of who I am, considering your own approach to dealing with problems.  I appreciate someone who is bold enough to take care of a situation in the most efficient manner.  With that said, I offer you an opportunity to, as you would put it, 'bring justice' to Ghost Widow of the Arachnos syndicate.  It seems she was overly eager to acquire a special device of mine, and is now in a rather weakened state.  Now's your chance to take care of her without any overly emotional heroes chastising you for your choices you make.'<br><br>The message ends with the location of where Ghost Widow is supposedly at.  This is obviously a trap, but for who?  It doesn't matter... someone will be brought to justice by the day's end.<br><br><color orange>WARNING: This is a Morality Mission. Completing this mission will change your alignment to Vigilante. This means that the people of Paragon City will no longer see you as a Hero. Becoming a Vigilante means you will gain the ability to travel to the Rogue Isles, once you've completed this mission.</color>"
// Answer Text :
"P1552923957" "Bring Justice to Ghost Widow without the eyes of the law on you."
// Page ImHero Text :
"P2592570333" "<color orange>WARNING: This is a Morality Mission. Completing this mission will change your current alignment of Hero to Vigilante, removing any progress you may have made on any other alignment. Becoming a Vigilante means you will be able to travel to the Rogue Isles.<br><br>Are you sure you want to do this?</color>"
// Answer Text :
"P2199002812" "Yes, I want to bring Justice to Ghost Widow without the eyes of the law on you."
// Answer Text :
"P2645858695" "On second thought, I'll hold off on this at the moment."
// Page ImVigilante Text :
"P2259632774" "<color orange>WARNING: This is a Morality Mission. Completing this mission will maintain your current alignment of Vigilante, removing any progress you may have made on any other alignments.<br><br>Are you sure you want to do this?</color>"
// Page PlayerBusy Text :
"P2220280554" "You don't have time to read today's paper."
